title: The Beatles - Public Domain Tracks, 1961-1962
description:
This is a compilation of the tracks by The Beatles that are in Public Domain in European Union since January 1 2013. If you are living in EU you can publish this recordings without paying any royalties and without asking any permission from EMI. All tracks are taken from the best sourses that are avaliable (more info can be found it the txt-file inside the torrent).
